{"tid":1346223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全力支持嶺大學生會罷免何君妖校董一職","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:47:24.000Z","uid":208319,"like":94,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"031599b69bc2ec586f3cc273a0874c8f0b93de46","tid":1346223,"uid":208319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/COWJe4y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCOWJe4y.png&h=040e0ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nlingu仔係時候做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5a7fcb1c6c70637545477ffa99e897e7ad12a7","tid":1346223,"uid":208319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:46:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3e507175e6a66a6c2a7cfee7428f02ff6da8eb","tid":1346223,"uid":208319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:47:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa7fb6ebb6e84ee0e70ec0de7c339731dff2b625","tid":1346223,"uid":208319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:47:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49ee4d97689e17f3880192d308141a426ea5d189","tid":1346223,"uid":208319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:48:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3c3464b8d38670dfc75b531a44cbbe1bb186467","tid":1346223,"uid":208319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"239e2d327faa4371c61455521ca83e972221c60d","tid":1346223,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:48:37.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"afa8aecf75d168f3d546ca6157b628ddb9bf5f40","tid":1346223,"uid":68471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:48:41.000Z","msg":"近千名元朗白衣人在元朗雞地及西鐵站內，手持長傘、竹枝及鐵通，追打身穿黑衣人士。元朗區議員黃偉賢今早在電台節目中表示，他昨日亦在元朗現場，當時，有白衣人向著他的方向，呼喊要打他，他隨即向警方求助，惟警方拒理，並驅車離開。他以「無法無天」來形容白衣人及警方昨晚的行動，並計劃今日到元朗警署抗議。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，昨晚與另一名元朗區議員杜嘉倫在元朗現場，當時有十多部衝鋒車在附近。其後有一部私家車停下來，並跳出幾名白衣人，衝向他並說要打他。他隨即拍打旁邊警車的車門，坐在司機位的警員隨即校低車窗，詢問他發生什麼事。他說︰「我是元朗區議員，這幾位白衣人說想打我，我要求保護。」他指，該名警員聽到後，隨即校回玻璃窗，拒絕受理並開車離開。就有關情況，TOPick正向警方查詢，暫未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n對於有市民指昨晚一直未見警方在現場執法，黃偉賢指，在晚上七時許，已有街坊致電報警表示有大批白衣人在元朗YOHO一帶聚集，但卻被警方CUT線。惟警方卻指稱在晚上十時四十一分才收到報案。他形容︰「警方都無法無天，根本就係放水。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，有市民亦致電電台指，目擊昨晚港鐵元朗站襲擊事件。他表示當時警方看著一批白衣人士離開，但卻沒有採取拘捕行動，只是舉起警棍大聲叫。他指，當時該批白衣人手持棍和藤條，在警員面前行過，而市民則大叫「打人」，但警方向沒有任何執法行動。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2407150/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2407150%2F&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=28de9dc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2407150/</a>"},{"pid":"79df235b9935550d6756c402191e8dccc84a947a","tid":1346223,"uid":208319,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:49:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41090d1cfb430d13fe10c10e5b781e87c2607a93","tid":1346223,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:49:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"47394cab522f9e39de377e9374085c75a4bd8284","tid":1346223,"uid":208319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:49:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f4cb928c92adb508c9295572d2c55d3cd26ff093","tid":1346223,"uid":208319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:50:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"566ab5a616744370a6b97f8c567cf3ac1d934fda","tid":1346223,"uid":208319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:50:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f364732ed4709283bf2ea1591e2584cdd149bcd5","tid":1346223,"uid":282537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"031599b69bc2ec586f3cc273a0874c8f0b93de46","tid